stylometry: Data mining is the act of gathering a data set, analyzing it, clustering it, and using the clusters to predict or dictate how a business is run. This is important to business because by grouping like customers (for example) the business can figure out what type of customers they have and how better to serve them. Different customers may have difffernt spending capabilities and different consumer expectations. By grouping(clustering) these customers together the business simplifies it's strategic goals in meeting customer needs.
